wiki.content: Speaking to MTV News prior to the song's release, Clarkson said the inspiring dance anthem reminded her of one of her own all-time favorites. "That'll be the one [that's] kinda like 'Since U Been Gone,' [with] people jumping up and down to [it], and it's just kind of really inspiring, so I can't wait to perform that one," she said. (Source What Doesn't Kill You (Stronger) Songfacts). User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
